    },
    "summary": {
        "overview": "This protocol provides a comprehensive guide for identifying and characterizing myeloid and lymphoid cell subtypes in DDLPS tumors using scRNA-seq, immunohistochemistry, in situ multiplex immunofluorescence, flow cytometry, and functional assays. Each step is designed to ensure accuracy, reliability, and alignment with the overall content and objectives of the paper.",
        "conclusion": "The detailed steps, explicit references to the original text, and alignment with the paper's objectives ensure a thorough and reliable protocol for characterizing the cellular heterogeneity of DDLPS and its microenvironment."
